Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:58.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has it been two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:28.65,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1\NBalsa, the Female Bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and swing your plows!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:37.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sow the rice seeds\Nand make the seedlings sprout!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:44.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nahji, come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:52.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Swarm like a black cloud and\Nfly down from the northern mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to be in Yogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel my soul\Ngrowing more tranquil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often that you\Nsee a woman warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from Kanbal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:26.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes. I'm here for\Nmaintenance on my short spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maintenance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:33.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, unlike Kanbal, you can\Nget anything you need in Yogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's assuming, of course,\Nthat you have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But those with money end up\Nliving the same life wherever they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:47.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Having none, however, means\Nyou can live as those around you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And there's really nothing\Nwrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite philosophical\Nfor someone so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not young any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be 30 this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:18.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a royal family procession!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not from this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no obligation whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:06.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must've lost\Nconsciousness right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't swallow any water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commoners such as you must never\Nlook upon one of the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not look at him!\NHurry, send for a carriage and doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, send for a carriage and doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Get rid of that crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling it was you, Tanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:03.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For you to come all\Nthe way to Ogi no Shimo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gather she hasn't come here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:12.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tanda.\NBut it's been two years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:15.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised if Balsa\Ncame back any day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come inside, Tanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:26.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll visit with you some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:31.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have an order for medicinal herbs,\Nso I'll be in town for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we hear anything about Balsa,\Nyou'll be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they read this\Nwould-be hero the riot act!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe the gall of that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:51.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sake! Bring us some more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sake! Bring us some more sake!\NHere you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:53.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sake! Bring us some more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is something\Nwe'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that a warrior\Nrescued a member...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...of the royal family\Nfrom Aoyumi River today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are searching for this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that this warrior\Nwas a short-spear bearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you happen to know\Nanything of this warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget we had this conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you don't\Nwant me to just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:16.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With your skills, you'd be killed twice\Nbefore your sword was drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:17.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I realize we have\Nacted with disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are emissaries from the court...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and have been searching for you\Non orders of the second queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:28.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The second queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:31.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that it was a skilled\Nwarrior who saved the prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we assumed it was a man,\Nand have only been questioning men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:37.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I am now convinced\Nthat this warrior was, in fact, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have my word\Nthat we will do you no harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:44.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, do us the honor of\Naccompanying us to Ninomiya Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not what I had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should've had this repaired\Nas soon as I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:04.99,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:37.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this palace is so lavish, the mikado's\Nlifestyle must be beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate to see this feast go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:05.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, why would\Nthey poison me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:14.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us for not being more\Neffusive after inviting you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:19.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A foreigner such as yourself\Nmight not be aware of this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We commoners are unable\Nto look directly into the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...of a member of the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, we will instantly\Nbe struck blind in both eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is one of the reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:38.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the second queen is most\Ngrateful to you for saving the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This money is your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:47.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The amount is paltry for the life\Nof a prince, but please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:52.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Her Majesty the\Nsecond queen herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:57.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...has instructed me to ask you\Nto spend the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have already done\Nmore than enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:09.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, do us the honor\Nof staying the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your belongings have been\Ntaken to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:14.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, what on earth\Nis this futon made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the nobility are called\N"those who dwell on the clouds"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...because they sleep on\Nthese huge things every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:59.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This may be my only chance to\Nexperience what they call "heaven"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warrior from another land...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm awake. Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:41.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you are indeed\Nas formidable a woman as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:48.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look us in the eye,\Nand yet you do not fall blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:56.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for\Nrescuing the prince today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have my deepest gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am unworthy of your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have already shown me\Nhospitality of the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:09.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any further gestures\Nare most unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:15.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I expect that you\Nmust find our coming to visit you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:18.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...in the middle of the night\Nto be most unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look up, Balsa. Show me your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:31.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as my attendants said,\Nyou have a fearless look in your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:36.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are known by the name\NBalsa the Spear-wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that there are none\Nwho do not know your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:43.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that you have the appearance\Nof a warrior of distant Kanbal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:47.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and that your skills have\Nsaved many lives over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:54.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you have heard are no more than\Nrumors that embellish my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:16:00.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am a bodyguard who protects\Nothers for money, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:01.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:14.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you risk your life\Nto earn money performing such work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:20.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, it is the hope\Nthat I place in your ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that has brought me\Nhere to ask this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not care where you flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take this child...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:32.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and protect him for the rest of\Nhis life from the mikado's assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:34.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the mikado's assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today it was an ox cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Half a month ago,\Nhe had a narrow escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...when a geyser suddenly\Nerupted at the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why in the world would\Nthe mikado want to kill the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It all began some two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:03.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night after night, the child began\Nmumbling strange things in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:08.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I had his tutor, a star reader,\Nobserve him as he slept...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:13.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...he told me that some unknown\Nforce had possessed the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:20.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, this star reader\Nis honorable and trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:26.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We told no one, turning instead\Nto a magic weaver of the Yakoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:31.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, the star reader consulted\Nnot only this magic weaver...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but the master star reader as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:42.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect that the mikado\Nsecretly ordered the prince's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:46.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...upon receiving\Nthe master star reader's counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merely for that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:53.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If word of this gets out\Nand rumors begin to spread...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:58.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it would irreparably damage\Nthe good name of the mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:09.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You! Have you been\Ndisrespectful to my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, she has not, Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:17.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have asked her to\Nsafeguard your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:18.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But wait a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, you must listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From this moment on, I want you\Nto follow her wherever she goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:30.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and no matter what happens,\Nyou must not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:36.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You ceased to be a prince the instant\Nthe mikado ordered your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you must not harbor\Nill will towards the mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:45.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He bears the terrible responsibility\Nof ruling this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:11.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A commoner could not spend all\Nthis in a lifetime, try as she might.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:16.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me your word that you\Nwill accept this and protect my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:22.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, I understand the gist\Nof your request. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:27.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a most dishonorable\Nway for you to treat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:35.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For my life to be forfeit as a reward\Nfor having saved the prince's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is that not dishonorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one is suggesting\Nthat you be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If someone of my low social status\Nwere to hear a story such as yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that person would have no choice\Nbut to agree to your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:57.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet once she agreed, her life\Nwould be more or less in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:02.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you are too unfamiliar with\Nthe ways of the world, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever tried to pay for something\Nwith gems bearing this palace crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...our whereabouts would be\Ndiscovered at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:14.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. However, this is the only money\Nthat I have at my disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you are correct.\NI cannot allow one who has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...learned this secret to leave\Nwithout consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:29.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa! You can either die here or take\Na chance at survival with the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:31.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choose one or the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:40.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you certainly don't seem to\Nhave many trustworthy men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two in the room behind me.\NThree in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Counting these two, you have\Nseven in all, which is quite pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:58.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:03.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I'll take the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:05.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fill this with as much as will fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:15.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, earlier you asked\Nwhy it is that I work as a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:21.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, I was forced to take\Nthe lives of eight dear people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, to appease the souls\Nof those eight people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:31.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I am working as a bodyguard until\NI've saved an equal number of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eight people's souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:36.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:45.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go with her, Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust her as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:51.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:55.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to go! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:16.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You! If you want the prince\Nto escape to safety...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...start by setting a fire\Nin his bedchamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:22.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then take us to the\Npalace's secret escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:29.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hand me the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:35.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:36.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you include my son's life,\Nhow many lives will you have saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:47.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, his life will be the eighth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:44.95,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.61,0:24:44.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa goes into hiding in the Yogo city.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:48.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she and Chagum\Nare given no time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.38,0:24:52.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Hunters, Hunted."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2\NHunters, Hunted
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.52,0:24:54.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mikado's shadow servants...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.76,0:24:57.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...are about to be unleashed.
